'''Blackhole''' was a code name used in [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Its first user was [[Lord/Legends|Lord]] [[Cronal]], former [[Prophets of the Dark Side|Prophet of the Dark Side]], when he became [[Director of Imperial Intelligence]]. Following Cronal's [[Death/Legends|death]] at the [[Battle of Mindor]], the code name was inherited by [[Grand Vizier/Legends|Grand Vizier]] [[Sate Pestage/Legends|Sate Pestage]], who co-opted this façade as a cover for himself while helping Palpatine return to power in a [[Cloning/Legends|clone]] body and establish his [[Dark Empire]].

